1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:18,430 --> 00:01:24,960
[Flight to You]

3
00:01:28,330 --> 00:01:30,680
[Episode 26]

4
00:01:32,460 --> 00:01:33,120
Well,

5
00:01:33,490 --> 00:01:35,020
where should I keep the key?

6
00:01:36,490 --> 00:01:37,050
No need.

7
00:01:37,630 --> 00:01:38,830
I'll change the lock.

8
00:01:55,690 --> 00:01:57,090
Brother Zhan, thank you.

9
00:01:57,229 --> 00:01:59,090
I'll treat you to dinner tonight.

10
00:01:59,620 --> 00:02:01,150
I really want to rip you off.

11
00:02:01,390 --> 00:02:02,040
You owe me.

12
00:02:03,190 --> 00:02:04,800
I have to go back to the hangar.

13
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:07,330
We have to stay up late because of a tough task.

14
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:09,360
Why do you always stay up late?

15
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:10,900
It's bad for your health.

16
00:02:10,949 --> 00:02:12,850
That's what I do. I'm used to it.

17
00:02:13,990 --> 00:02:14,710
Besides,

18
00:02:14,860 --> 00:02:16,140
I have to strive for

19
00:02:16,390 --> 00:02:18,850
the vice president position of the company.

20
00:02:19,350 --> 00:02:21,220
Are you and Mr. Gu

21
00:02:21,650 --> 00:02:22,710
serious this time?

22
00:02:22,890 --> 00:02:23,540
Of course.

23
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:26,900
He has his dreams and I have my ambitions.

24
00:02:27,829 --> 00:02:28,240
What?

25
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,740
Are you afraid of me losing

26
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,030
or Nanting?

27
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:34,930
Sure enough.

28
00:02:35,420 --> 00:02:36,670
You are frenemies.

29
00:02:38,310 --> 00:02:40,020
Fair competition won't hurt our relationship.

30
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:40,750
Don't worry.

31
00:02:42,370 --> 00:02:43,100
I'm leaving.

32
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:43,820
Okay.

33
00:02:44,620 --> 00:02:45,770
Bye. Thank you.

34
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,350
Goodbye, Mr. Ni. Goodbye.

35
00:02:47,350 --> 00:02:47,650
Bye.

36
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,579
Bye. Bye.

37
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,750
I'll shut it. Go ahead.

38
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,390
It's okay.

39
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,520
It's been two days. But it feels like

40
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,810
there's no progress.

41
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,460
This is really...

42
00:03:35,380 --> 00:03:37,000
The flight was delayed last night, right?

43
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,730
Why don't you go home and sleep?

44
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,500
I'll go back after eating.

45
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,120
The efficiency of your Flight Department

46
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,440
is too low.

47
00:03:45,470 --> 00:03:46,530
It's been two days.

48
00:03:46,850 --> 00:03:48,910
You haven't rehabilitated Xiao yet.

49
00:03:50,340 --> 00:03:50,950
I think

50
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,840
the higher-ups want to

51
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,260
settle this by leaving it unsettled.

52
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:55,850
How can we investigate

53
00:03:56,390 --> 00:03:57,990
the hearsay on the Internet?

54
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,720
Who would spread rumours here for no reason?

55
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:01,180
Well...

56
00:04:01,290 --> 00:04:02,530
The suspect must be

57
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:03,850
one of Xiao's enemies.

58
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:07,870
I didn't hear anyone has a grudge against Xiao.

59
00:04:08,970 --> 00:04:10,770
It may not be against Cheng Xiao.

60
00:04:10,950 --> 00:04:11,640
This matter also has a great impact

61
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:13,970
on Brother Nanting and Mr. Ni.

62
00:04:15,540 --> 00:04:18,600
Don't let it affect their promotion to vice president.

63
00:04:24,430 --> 00:04:25,590
Could it be

64
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,660
Mr. Jiang?

65
00:04:28,530 --> 00:04:30,990
How dare you make up stories about your boss?

66
00:04:34,909 --> 00:04:35,520
I think

67
00:04:37,030 --> 00:04:38,190
there's someone else.

68
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:38,920
-Who?
-Who?

69
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,010
Do you mean this?

70
00:04:55,810 --> 00:04:56,770
It is possible.

71
00:04:57,659 --> 00:04:58,730
But in theory,

72
00:04:58,830 --> 00:05:01,260
I should be the one Qi Yu hates the most.

73
00:05:02,330 --> 00:05:04,460
Although that rumor also involves me,

74
00:05:04,530 --> 00:05:06,460
it doesn't seem to be targeting me.

75
00:05:11,340 --> 00:05:12,070
Wait for me.

76
00:05:12,300 --> 00:05:12,830
Okay.

77
00:05:14,940 --> 00:05:15,730
Coming.

78
00:05:16,430 --> 00:05:17,160
Xia, Yuheng.

79
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,840
Our handsome Captain Song is here too.

80
00:05:20,840 --> 00:05:22,170
No, no, no, I am not the captain.

81
00:05:22,170 --> 00:05:23,500
I'm only a junior pilot.

82
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:28,170
Is your hand recovered?

83
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:30,790
Yes.

84
00:05:31,130 --> 00:05:32,930
Today is the first day of flying.

85
00:05:33,420 --> 00:05:34,050
Xiazhi.

86
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,860
I haven't officially apologized to you.

87
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:39,159
I was angry that day

88
00:05:40,010 --> 00:05:41,700
and caused you suffering.

89
00:05:42,270 --> 00:05:42,940
I'm sorry.

90
00:05:44,990 --> 00:05:46,360
Don't say that, Qi Yu.

91
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,409
It's all about work.

92
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:50,980
It's good that you've made it clear.

93
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:52,270
Qi Yu,

94
00:05:52,909 --> 00:05:55,770
are you still blaming me for what happened that day?

95
00:05:55,790 --> 00:05:56,440
Of course.

96
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:01,610
I was demoted from a trainee chief flight attendant.

97
00:06:09,940 --> 00:06:11,470
I was really angry that day.

98
00:06:11,690 --> 00:06:13,690
But when I got home, I figured it out.

99
00:06:13,930 --> 00:06:14,920
I was too muddleheaded

100
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,580
to argue with the passengers.

101
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:21,200
Yuheng, you actually helped me.

102
00:06:21,580 --> 00:06:22,240
Otherwise,

103
00:06:22,250 --> 00:06:24,180
if I made a bigger mistake that day,

104
00:06:24,460 --> 00:06:26,120
it would be too late to regret.

105
00:06:27,510 --> 00:06:28,830
Qi Yu, what you said...

106
00:06:28,850 --> 00:06:29,410
Yuheng.

107
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:33,040
You performed well and were promoted at a fast pace.

108
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,170
I may be demoted now,

109
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,830
but when I am promoted to chief flight attendant,

110
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:38,430
I'm definitely ahead of you.

111
00:06:40,270 --> 00:06:41,270
Don't be jealous.

112
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:42,710
Of course not.

113
00:06:44,340 --> 00:06:45,270
Enjoy your meal.

114
00:06:45,350 --> 00:06:46,080
I'm leaving.

115
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:55,850
Do you think

116
00:06:56,770 --> 00:06:57,580
it is her?

117
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,080
Don't touch that.

118
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:24,850
I'm sorry.

119
00:07:27,190 --> 00:07:29,250
I'm sorry. I didn't mean it.

120
00:07:29,780 --> 00:07:30,380
I'm sorry.

121
00:07:32,900 --> 00:07:33,650
It's okay.

122
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,250
Sorry.

123
00:07:35,750 --> 00:07:37,040
I have a loud voice.

124
00:07:38,290 --> 00:07:39,760
You may work on something else.

125
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:40,360
Sorry.

126
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:29,010
I heard from Nanting

127
00:10:29,250 --> 00:10:30,980
you've been doing well lately.

128
00:10:31,550 --> 00:10:32,680
You're really good.

129
00:10:33,830 --> 00:10:34,500
Brother Nanting

130
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:36,300
has been encouraging me at work.

131
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:39,170
And my leaders and colleagues at the Cabin Service Department

132
00:10:39,170 --> 00:10:40,830
have been helping me.

133
00:10:41,410 --> 00:10:42,870
But take care of yourself.

134
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,570
You look slimmer.

135
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,400
I've been flying international flights lately.

136
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:48,860
I always have jet lag,

137
00:10:49,110 --> 00:10:50,640
so I can't sleep quite well.

138
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:52,510
I heard that

139
00:10:52,610 --> 00:10:54,870
you rented a house with your colleagues.

140
00:10:55,790 --> 00:10:57,630
I wanted to live alone before.

141
00:10:57,900 --> 00:10:58,450
But

142
00:10:58,770 --> 00:11:01,260
a house with a suitable location and condition

143
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:02,530
is really hard to find.

144
00:11:02,810 --> 00:11:04,210
Nanting has a house.

145
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,750
His tenant just moved out.

146
00:11:06,020 --> 00:11:07,420
You can move to his place.

147
00:11:08,250 --> 00:11:09,000
Can I?

148
00:11:09,260 --> 00:11:10,430
Of course.

149
00:11:10,540 --> 00:11:12,030
The house is empty.

150
00:11:12,450 --> 00:11:13,790
But let's make a deal.

151
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:15,920
I won't accept your rent.

152
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:17,400
It's too kind of you.

153
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:19,100
I must pay the rent.

154
00:11:19,130 --> 00:11:21,110
We watched you grow up.

155
00:11:21,140 --> 00:11:21,880
How can we

156
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:23,390
accept your rent with this relationship?

157
00:11:23,390 --> 00:11:24,110
Thank you, auntie.

158
00:11:24,110 --> 00:11:25,620
But I must pay the rent.

159
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:27,030
Otherwise, I won't move there.

160
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:27,800
Look.

161
00:11:28,620 --> 00:11:30,360
I'll give you a 50% discount.

162
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,120
It's settled. You can't argue anymore.

163
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,180
Thank you, auntie.

164
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,930
Here, have some coffee.

165
00:11:35,130 --> 00:11:36,520
We were just talking about it.

166
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:38,640
Didn't your tenant just move out?

167
00:11:38,640 --> 00:11:40,080
Xiao Yu wants to rent a house.

168
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,540
Let her live in your house.

169
00:11:45,570 --> 00:11:46,170
You...

170
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:49,180
don't live with Xiazhi anymore?

171
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:52,410
We often don't fly together.

172
00:11:52,530 --> 00:11:54,190
We tend to disturb each other.

173
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,170
Auntie Qin said

174
00:11:55,190 --> 00:11:56,320
you could rent that house to me.

175
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,710
I think it is a good idea.

176
00:11:57,850 --> 00:12:00,250
After all, it's not easy to find a house now.

177
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:05,270
Let me help you find a place.

178
00:12:09,420 --> 00:12:09,820
Mom.

179
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:12,180
I don't want to rent that place

180
00:12:12,470 --> 00:12:13,530
for the time being.

181
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:15,120
Why?

182
00:12:21,450 --> 00:12:22,840
It's okay, Brother Nanting.

183
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:23,440
Don't bother.

184
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:24,760
I'll continue to

185
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:25,760
stay with Xiazhi.

186
00:12:30,270 --> 00:12:30,890
I'm sorry.

187
00:12:40,650 --> 00:12:41,910
I'll get some tissues.

188
00:12:47,770 --> 00:12:49,180
What's going on?

189
00:12:51,970 --> 00:12:52,870
Maybe

190
00:12:53,410 --> 00:12:54,450
the last tenant

191
00:12:55,560 --> 00:12:57,760
was too impressive to Brother Nanting.

192
00:13:01,230 --> 00:13:02,410
The last tenant...

193
00:14:58,310 --> 00:14:59,180
Polly.

194
00:16:23,830 --> 00:16:25,090
Take off your jewelry.

195
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:29,420
Wearing it won't affect my operation.

196
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:32,240
The company also doesn't have rules stating I can't wear it.

197
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:32,970
It is my rule.

198
00:16:34,160 --> 00:16:35,220
Please take it off.

199
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:49,240
Don't you have a pocket?

200
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:51,170
Zhang.

201
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:53,170
Yes, it's me.

202
00:17:54,180 --> 00:17:55,770
I want to ask you a favor.

203
00:17:56,460 --> 00:17:58,420
Didn't I rent my house out?

204
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:00,850
The tenant canceled the lease a few days ago.

205
00:18:00,850 --> 00:18:03,430
I suddenly recalled something that I need to contact her about.

206
00:18:03,430 --> 00:18:05,530
I can't remember her name.

207
00:18:07,990 --> 00:18:08,570
Right.

208
00:18:09,550 --> 00:18:10,770
Cheng Xiao, yes.

209
00:18:16,780 --> 00:18:17,350
OK.

210
00:18:18,150 --> 00:18:19,080
Okay, thank you.

211
00:18:19,490 --> 00:18:22,710
[Cheng]

212
00:18:25,120 --> 00:18:25,800
This girl...

213
00:18:25,800 --> 00:18:27,640
I saw her

214
00:18:28,360 --> 00:18:29,590
when I was in Xi'an last time.

215
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:31,250
You said she was your student.

216
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:33,670
Yes, her name is Cheng Xiao.

217
00:18:34,620 --> 00:18:35,360
Cheng Xiao.

218
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,240
Are you two close?

219
00:18:39,470 --> 00:18:41,330
No, mom, you think too much.

220
00:18:42,380 --> 00:18:43,310
What did I think?

221
00:18:58,350 --> 00:19:04,310
[One week later]

222
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:19,670
Hello.

223
00:19:20,050 --> 00:19:20,840
Hello, Mr. Gu.

224
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:22,170
I'm Chen on flight duty.

225
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:23,400
Captain Fan of

226
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:25,280
flight 8273 to Xi'an

227
00:19:25,490 --> 00:19:27,620
suddenly had diarrhea and took a sick leave.

228
00:19:27,620 --> 00:19:28,410
8273?

229
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:30,180
Yes, at 8:30 p.m.

230
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:32,000
Hold on.

231
00:19:32,650 --> 00:19:34,650
Let me check those who are off today.

232
00:19:46,780 --> 00:19:48,930
[Cheng Xiao]

233
00:19:53,570 --> 00:19:54,430
How about this?

234
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:56,090
I'll take this flight.

235
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:57,050
Mr. Gu.

236
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:59,300
Cheng Xiao will take this flight.

237
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:01,600
You asked us

238
00:20:01,770 --> 00:20:02,640
to minimize...

239
00:20:02,740 --> 00:20:04,400
The situation is special today.

240
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:06,120
Those who are off are not qualified to lead the flying.

241
00:20:06,120 --> 00:20:06,720
I'll do it.

242
00:20:34,460 --> 00:20:36,190
Captain Fan hasn't arrived yet.

243
00:20:36,190 --> 00:20:36,970
Is it okay?

244
00:20:37,470 --> 00:20:38,370
I think so.

245
00:20:54,650 --> 00:20:55,990
Captain Fan is not feeling well.

246
00:20:55,990 --> 00:20:57,190
I'll take over today.

247
00:21:10,630 --> 00:21:11,690
Let's get started.

248
00:21:12,820 --> 00:21:14,360
Glad to fly with you guys.

249
00:21:14,380 --> 00:21:16,130
Flight XD8273

250
00:21:16,150 --> 00:21:17,350
from Luzhou to Xi'an.

251
00:21:34,390 --> 00:21:36,570
Drink the coffee quickly. Don't spill it.

252
00:21:36,570 --> 00:21:37,430
It's not for me.

253
00:21:38,750 --> 00:21:40,350
I'm not drinking it, thanks.

254
00:21:41,500 --> 00:21:42,830
It's not for you either.

255
00:21:49,030 --> 00:21:49,730
Captains.

256
00:21:50,040 --> 00:21:51,990
The plane is in good condition. There has no retention breakdown.

257
00:21:51,990 --> 00:21:53,140
Brother Fan, come on.

258
00:21:53,140 --> 00:21:54,140
Have some coffee.

259
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:55,000
Thank you.

260
00:21:55,700 --> 00:21:57,030
How embarrassing it is.

261
00:21:57,030 --> 00:21:58,030
Don't mention it.

262
00:22:00,830 --> 00:22:01,530
Sign this.

263
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:08,580
Captain Cheng,

264
00:22:08,670 --> 00:22:09,870
you are as meticulous

265
00:22:10,260 --> 00:22:11,190
as Brother Zhan.

266
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:14,670
If the plane is in good condition,

267
00:22:14,670 --> 00:22:15,870
we're ready to board.

268
00:22:16,040 --> 00:22:16,840
Yes, captain.

269
00:22:23,110 --> 00:22:24,940
I've been working night shifts lately.

270
00:22:24,940 --> 00:22:26,220
I'm losing all my hair.

271
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:30,600
Just think that you have saved the shampoo.

272
00:22:31,410 --> 00:22:32,010
Get ready.

273
00:22:35,060 --> 00:22:36,190
Hello, passengers.

274
00:22:36,260 --> 00:22:37,440
Passengers of Luzhou Airlines

275
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:39,460
flight XD8273

276
00:22:39,480 --> 00:22:41,280
to Xi'an, please pay attention.

277
00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:43,720
The flight you're taking is now boarding.

278
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:45,360
Please take your belongings

279
00:22:45,410 --> 00:22:46,400
and show your boarding pass

280
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:48,890
at Gate 79 for boarding.

281
00:22:48,970 --> 00:22:50,230
First-class passengers, platinum cardholders

282
00:22:50,230 --> 00:22:51,850
and those who need special care,

283
00:22:51,850 --> 00:22:53,580
please board first. Thank you.

284
00:22:55,170 --> 00:22:55,690
Hello.

285
00:22:55,720 --> 00:22:56,660
Welcome aboard.

286
00:22:57,060 --> 00:22:57,450
Hello.

287
00:22:57,450 --> 00:22:59,000
Please go straight and turn left.

288
00:22:59,000 --> 00:22:59,930
Welcome aboard.

289
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:01,560
Please go straight and turn left.

290
00:23:01,560 --> 00:23:03,530
Welcome aboard. Please turn right.

291
00:23:03,530 --> 00:23:05,160
