00:37:48,980 --> 00:37:50,440
you shouldn't be so harsh.

582
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:53,500
I'm sorry

583
00:37:54,620 --> 00:37:55,350
for Wang Fan.

584
00:37:57,070 --> 00:37:58,560
But I won't be lenient

585
00:37:58,590 --> 00:38:00,650
just because he's your subordinate.

586
00:38:00,680 --> 00:38:02,000
This is a typical case.

587
00:38:02,240 --> 00:38:03,940
We should look into the unsafe factors.

588
00:38:03,940 --> 00:38:05,340
That's why I reported it.

589
00:38:07,120 --> 00:38:08,330
Wang Fan fractured his bone.

590
00:38:08,330 --> 00:38:09,860
He is lying in the hospital.

591
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:12,400
Do you know his family situation?

592
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:14,060
His wife is a full-time housewife.

593
00:38:14,060 --> 00:38:15,190
He has two children.

594
00:38:15,200 --> 00:38:16,800
He's already pretty hard up.

595
00:38:17,160 --> 00:38:19,090
Now he can't work for three months.

596
00:38:20,200 --> 00:38:22,010
According to our system,

597
00:38:22,040 --> 00:38:23,510
we would deduct his bonus for three months,

598
00:38:23,510 --> 00:38:25,570
demote him and cut his salary by half.

599
00:38:25,860 --> 00:38:27,050
Isn't that enough?

600
00:38:27,730 --> 00:38:29,260
But because of your report,

601
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:30,740
he may be fired.

602
00:38:33,710 --> 00:38:34,310
I'm sorry.

603
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:36,790
This matter

604
00:38:37,540 --> 00:38:39,430
will circulate a notice of criticism.

605
00:38:39,430 --> 00:38:40,670
The performance of the entire Maintenance Department

606
00:38:40,670 --> 00:38:41,680
will be affected.

607
00:38:41,720 --> 00:38:43,320
Just because of your report.

608
00:38:46,890 --> 00:38:48,950
You didn't mean to report it, did you?

609
00:38:54,540 --> 00:38:56,140
There are three months left before

610
00:38:56,140 --> 00:38:57,390
the vice president's election.

611
00:38:57,390 --> 00:38:59,240
Any mistake between you and me

612
00:38:59,700 --> 00:39:00,500
may affect

613
00:39:00,520 --> 00:39:01,520
the final result.

614
00:39:04,040 --> 00:39:04,520
Ni Zhan.

615
00:39:05,680 --> 00:39:07,800
We've known each other for more than ten years.

616
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:09,560
I thought no one was more clear about

617
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:11,400
what kind of person I am than you.

618
00:39:16,660 --> 00:39:17,480
I thought

619
00:39:18,720 --> 00:39:20,050
I knew you very well too.

620
00:39:20,580 --> 00:39:21,340
But now,

621
00:39:25,200 --> 00:39:27,600
sometimes I feel that you're strange to me.

622
00:40:04,640 --> 00:40:06,170
You were hurt to this state.

623
00:40:06,430 --> 00:40:08,800
The pilots flew away without a word like that.

624
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,570
Earning such a high salary,

625
00:40:10,970 --> 00:40:13,030
they don't know what we've suffered.

626
00:40:13,910 --> 00:40:15,110
Don't talk nonsense.

627
00:40:15,600 --> 00:40:16,680
I fell on my own.

628
00:40:17,020 --> 00:40:18,820
It has nothing to do with others.

629
00:40:19,320 --> 00:40:21,940
Why did they report it to the company if there's nothing to do with them?

630
00:40:21,940 --> 00:40:23,380
It's not the first time.

631
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:25,540
Last time, one of them

632
00:40:25,560 --> 00:40:26,300
braked late.

633
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:28,640
The plane slipped a bit forward.

634
00:40:28,990 --> 00:40:31,470
Eventually, the maintenance team was accused of giving the wrong command.

635
00:40:31,470 --> 00:40:32,900
It's not the same.

636
00:40:40,900 --> 00:40:41,960
Captain Gu is here.

637
00:40:42,200 --> 00:40:42,730
Wang Fan.

638
00:40:44,350 --> 00:40:45,550
I'm here to visit you.

639
00:40:46,330 --> 00:40:48,170
Thank you, Captain Gu. Sorry to make you spend so much money.

640
00:40:48,170 --> 00:40:48,660
It's OK.

641
00:40:49,750 --> 00:40:50,410
Let me do it.

642
00:40:52,960 --> 00:40:54,090
How was the surgery?

643
00:40:54,680 --> 00:40:55,450
It went well.

644
00:40:55,790 --> 00:40:57,120
I'm waiting to recover.

645
00:40:57,230 --> 00:40:58,560
Have a seat, Captain Gu.

646
00:40:58,920 --> 00:40:59,250
OK.

647
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:10,370
Brother Fan.

648
00:41:10,540 --> 00:41:11,800
Captain Cheng is here.

649
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:13,340
I brought you something.

650
00:41:13,560 --> 00:41:14,440
Thank you.

651
00:41:15,300 --> 00:41:16,490
You see, my falling

652
00:41:17,270 --> 00:41:18,680
caused you so much trouble.

653
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:20,160
Not at all.

654
00:41:30,160 --> 00:41:30,920
I'm sorry.

655
00:41:31,610 --> 00:41:33,470
My wife doesn't know the details.

656
00:41:33,760 --> 00:41:34,890
Don't care about it.

657
00:41:35,070 --> 00:41:36,130
It's not her fault.

658
00:41:36,500 --> 00:41:37,780
You got hurt because of work.

659
00:41:37,780 --> 00:41:39,510
Your family should be worried.

660
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:44,260
Brother Fan, how's your surgery?

661
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:45,270
It went well.

662
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:46,790
I'll be fine after a few days of hospitalization

663
00:41:46,790 --> 00:41:48,300
and recovering at home.

664
00:41:52,190 --> 00:41:52,850
Captain Gu,

665
00:41:53,610 --> 00:41:54,770
I sincerely apologize

666
00:41:54,770 --> 00:41:56,360
for what happened this time.

667
00:41:56,360 --> 00:41:57,820
It's indeed because I fell

668
00:41:57,830 --> 00:41:59,540
and tripped over the power line.

669
00:41:59,540 --> 00:42:00,500
Anyway,

670
00:42:01,050 --> 00:42:02,150
my mistake

671
00:42:02,550 --> 00:42:04,750
caused the passengers to feel shocked.

672
00:42:06,550 --> 00:42:08,610
Regarding the report to the company,

673
00:42:09,850 --> 00:42:11,310
I hope you can understand.

674
00:42:11,630 --> 00:42:12,960
Of course I understand.

675
00:42:15,080 --> 00:42:15,850
Actually,

676
00:42:17,410 --> 00:42:18,630
Mr. Gu has told the Security Department.

677
00:42:18,630 --> 00:42:20,490
Don't worry about anything else.

678
00:42:22,230 --> 00:42:23,160
Have a good rest.

679
00:42:25,280 --> 00:42:25,910
Sure.

680
00:42:35,090 --> 00:42:35,620
Okay.

681
00:42:36,500 --> 00:42:37,900
Have a rest. I'm leaving.

682
00:42:40,160 --> 00:42:40,760
Take care.

683
00:42:42,280 --> 00:42:43,810
Mind your step, Captain Gu.

684
00:42:48,020 --> 00:42:49,280
Captain Gu looks cold,

685
00:42:49,910 --> 00:42:51,240
but he's actually very caring.
